descr: "A structured set of questions intended to guide the collection of answers from end-users. Questionnaires provide detailed control over order, presentation, phraseology and grouping to allow coherent, consistent data collection."

fields.name: question
fields.descr: "The linkId for the question whose answer (or lack of answer) governs whether this item is enabled."

fields.name: hasAnswer
fields.descr: "An indication that this item should be enabled only if the specified question is answered (hasAnswer=true) or not answered (hasAnswer=false)."

fields.name: answerBoolean
